data.description: Just 2 miles from GA400 but tons of privacy, this beautiful 3 BR, 2 BA Ranch style home with in-ground pool, on almost 2 fenced in acres could be your own paradise. Close to shopping and restaurants, but not too close. Buyers will love the beautifully landscaped yard, the front porch and the back covered deck with lots of seating area just in time for football season.  The paved circular driveway brings you back to the house and the large workshop.  Entering the home you'll immediately notice the large 12" pine flooring as well as the exposed beams and shiplap in the living room, straight ahead is the kitchen and large dining room with lots of light from the many windows while viewing nature at its best. You can go out to the back deck and the pool area or go back to the hallway leading to three large bedrooms. Property is very private and has lots of space for storing boats, RV's or whatever you need to park. Bring your buyers, tell your friends, they aren't gonna want to miss out on this one!
